26
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:35,567
I want to be your friend!

27
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:40,033
You're so popular, Irie!

28
00:01:40,133 --> 00:01:41,333
No way.

29
00:01:43,933 --> 00:01:46,000
Can't we be friends?

30
00:01:50,133 --> 00:01:53,733
I don't want any stupid friends
from Class F.

31
