by our last conversation.

37
00:02:17,900 --> 00:02:20,000
I decided to "go for broke!"

38
00:02:20,500 --> 00:02:24,167
I see! And what did Yuki say?

39
00:02:26,200 --> 00:02:31,267
He'd think about it if I made
the top 100 on the upcoming test.

40
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:37,100
Really? Sounds exactly like
what I've been through!

41
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,700
But it's okay now.

42
00:02:39,767 --> 00:02:43,967
I think I'll give up on Yuki.

43
00:02:44,033 --> 00:02:45,367
What?

44
00:02:45,433 --> 00:02:50,767
I told Yuki how I felt.
That's enough for me.

45
00:02:51,933 --> 00:02:56,967
And I'll never make the top 100 anyway.

46
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:59,767
