117
00:08:54,667 --> 00:08:55,733
All right.

118
00:08:58,567 --> 00:09:00,733
Shall we start?

119
00:09:00,833 --> 00:09:01,833
Yes!

120
00:09:12,100 --> 00:09:13,033
What were you doing?

121
00:09:14,333 --> 00:09:16,500
I was just walking by.

122
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:20,833
Why don't you help her study?

123
00:09:21,467 --> 00:09:23,400
No way. She's too stupid.

124
00:09:24,733 --> 00:09:28,267
