if she makes the top 100.

125
00:09:30,933 --> 00:09:32,500
I see.

126
00:09:35,633 --> 00:09:37,100
So it's complicated.

127
00:09:37,167 --> 00:09:38,500
Not at all!

128
00:09:54,300 --> 00:09:55,467
Kotoko.

129
00:10:00,667 --> 00:10:01,800
Sorry.

130
00:10:06,167 --> 00:10:07,000
I...

