142
00:10:54,633 --> 00:10:59,167
We solved one problem.

143
00:10:59,233 --> 00:11:00,533
In three hours?

144
00:11:00,867 --> 00:11:01,700
Yes.

145
00:11:09,433 --> 00:11:10,500
How many pages?

146
00:11:13,667 --> 00:11:15,000
From here...

147
00:11:18,367 --> 00:11:19,867
to there.

148
00:11:22,733 --> 00:11:26,433
I can't let you waste more time.

149
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:30,600
It looks like you're in trouble.
I'll teach you.

150
00:11:31,167 --> 00:11:35,167
