152
00:11:46,533 --> 00:11:49,633
The answer is...

153
00:11:51,133 --> 00:11:55,800
2xy (3x - 2y...

154
00:11:55,900 --> 00:11:58,200
close parentheses?

155
00:12:00,067 --> 00:12:01,600
Correct.

156
00:12:01,667 --> 00:12:04,367
Wow! I did it!

157
00:12:08,533 --> 00:12:09,600
Hey!

158
00:12:14,067 --> 00:12:16,400
Naoki? Yuki?

159
00:12:17,767 --> 00:12:19,167
Was I sleeping?

160
00:12:20,567 --> 00:12:24,133
Stop bothering my brother.

161
00:12:25,933 --> 00:12:29,233
He's taking the National Medical
Board Examination soon.

162
00:12:29,400 --> 00:12:31,267
What are you gonna do if he fails?

163
00:12:39,167 --> 00:12:40,433
I'll teach you.

164
00:12:42,233 --> 00:12:45,267
We have one week until final exams.

165
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:50,767
I'll tutor you after school until 9 pm.

166
00:12:52,167 --> 00:12:53,433
Really?

167
00:12:58,300 --> 00:12:59,200
