168
00:13:00,233 --> 00:13:02,433
Yuki is tutoring Konomi?

169
00:13:05,700 --> 00:13:07,567
Thanks to you!

170
00:13:10,867 --> 00:13:13,700
I don't know what's going on, but...

171
00:13:18,100 --> 00:13:20,433
You got your foot in the door!

172
00:13:20,533 --> 00:13:26,400
Now kill two birds with one stone!
Love and exams!

173
00:13:26,667 --> 00:13:27,833
Yes!

174
00:13:28,700 --> 00:13:31,000
You're starting to talk like mom...

175
00:13:31,267 --> 00:13:32,533
What?

176
00:13:34,267 --> 00:13:35,400
Nothing.

177
00:13:35,533 --> 00:13:38,533
<i>I'm feeling really fired up!</i>

178
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:40,733
<i>How exciting!</i>

179
00:13:44,400 --> 00:13:48,067
<i>Yuki's study sessions continued...</i>

180
00:14:08,667 --> 00:14:09,567
Hey!

181
00:14:13,700 --> 00:14:14,767
Correct.

182
00:14:14,867 --> 00:14:16,800
Really? Wow!

183
00:14:16,967 --> 00:14:18,400
We did it!

184
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:26,400
Next!

185
00:14:27,033 --> 00:14:28,133
Yes.

186
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:34,133
- 2y = 0.

187
00:14:34,233 --> 00:14:39,433
y + 3 x (- 2y + 3).

188
00:14:41,333 --> 00:14:42,767
Excuse me.

189
00:14:44,800 --> 00:14:46,300
<i>And today is the final day.</i>

190
00:14:47,500 --> 00:14:51,367
Konomi, Yuki. How about some tea?

191
00:14:51,467 --> 00:14:52,967
Thank you.

192
00:14:54,767 --> 00:14:56,233
How is it going?

193
00:14:56,300 --> 00:14:58,033
Fine, thank you.

194
00:14:58,100 --> 00:15:01,900
Yuki's a tough teacher.
Is he mean to you?

195
00:15:01,967 --> 00:15:03,767
Oh, no.

196
00:15:04,533 --> 00:15:06,300
I can't help it if she's stupid.

197
00:15:06,367 --> 00:15:08,967
Don't say that!

198
00:15:09,033 --> 00:15:13,133
Konomi, don't take it to heart.
Yuki may say that...

199
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:18,400
but boys are always mean
to girls they like.

200
00:15:18,467 --> 00:15:20,233
Is that true?

201
00:15:20,300 --> 00:15:21,967
Her? No way!

202
00:15:22,033 --> 00:15:24,533
There he goes again.

203
00:15:27,933 --> 00:15:29,967
Tadaa. Look at this.

204
00:15:30,033 --> 00:15:31,533
What's that?

205
00:15:31,600 --> 00:15:33,100
