208
00:15:52,100 --> 00:15:55,767
Look how he's staring at you.

209
00:15:56,300 --> 00:16:01,600
Don't be so stubborn, Yuki.
Just admit that you like her!

210
00:16:05,867 --> 00:16:08,567
You look so cute together!

211
00:16:09,333 --> 00:16:12,767
