215
00:16:23,800 --> 00:16:26,100
It's bad enough I have to tutor her.

216
00:16:26,633 --> 00:16:28,200
You took pictures as well?

217
00:16:29,367 --> 00:16:30,667
I...

218
00:16:31,367 --> 00:16:34,633
I'm not your plaything!

219
00:16:36,167 --> 00:16:37,433
