Yuki.

225
00:17:34,633 --> 00:17:36,233
You're a mess.

226
00:17:39,700 --> 00:17:40,733
Why?

227
00:17:41,367 --> 00:17:42,933
I promised.

228
00:17:44,733 --> 00:17:47,000
I'd tutor you every day

229
00:17:47,800 --> 00:17:50,900
until 9 p.m. for a week until the exam.

230
00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:54,667
