231
00:17:56,167 --> 00:17:57,900
Don't try to break my promise.

232
00:17:59,867 --> 00:18:01,633
Oh, yeah.

233
00:18:03,133 --> 00:18:04,133
Sorry.

234
00:18:15,033 --> 00:18:15,900
And...

235
00:18:18,867 --> 00:18:19,867
You forgot something.

236
00:18:29,233 --> 00:18:30,400
For good luck, right?

237
00:18:32,500 --> 00:18:33,433
Thank you!

238
00:18:39,467 --> 00:18:40,567
Let go!

239
00:18:40,667 --> 00:18:42,200
Look!

240
00:18:43,533 --> 00:18:44,500
All right.

241
00:18:44,733 --> 00:18:46,267
This one, too!

242
00:18:46,367 --> 00:18:49,200
Let go. We're going home.

243
00:18:49,600 --> 00:18:52,767
That's enough, already.

244
00:18:52,867 --> 00:18:57,100
But your mom asked me to.

245
00:18:57,433 --> 00:19:01,667
It looks like Yuki may take
the same path as me.

246
00:19:02,700 --> 00:19:03,633
Poor guy.

247
00:19:04,667 --> 00:19:07,500
What poor guy?

248
00:19:21,033 --> 00:19:24,767
Do you have your papers?
Your pencil case?

249
00:19:24,833 --> 00:19:25,667
Yeah.

250
00:19:25,733 --> 00:19:28,700
