together next year.

259
00:19:57,567 --> 00:20:00,700
It'll be fun! So don't worry!

260
00:20:00,800 --> 00:20:03,233
I don't intend to.

261
00:20:04,933 --> 00:20:06,100
See you.

262
00:20:08,167 --> 00:20:12,167
You can do it, Naoki!

263
00:20:25,233 --> 00:20:29,567
<i>The results of the National Exam</i>
<i>are going to be posted today.</i>

264
00:20:31,033 --> 00:20:35,100
Stop pacing back and forth
like a bear in a cage!

265
00:20:35,200 --> 00:20:37,300
But!

266
00:20:37,400 --> 00:20:41,733
The results will be posted
in one minute! I can't stay still!

267
00:20:41,833 --> 00:20:43,533
Calm down, Kotoko.

268
00:20:43,800 --> 00:20:47,667
Relax! Breathe in and out.

269
00:20:47,833 --> 00:20:49,233
